",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>ELPA is een onafhankelijke organisatie, gespecialiseerd op het gebied van verhuismanagement.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\",\"text_color\":\"#ffffff\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"fftyb35\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null,\"padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"50\",\"right\":\"75\",\"bottom\":\"20\",\"left\":\"75\",\"isLinked\":false},\"padding_tablet\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"50\",\"right\":\"25\",\"bottom\":\"20\",\"left\":\"25\",\"isLinked\":false},\"padding_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"50\",\"right\":\"50\",\"bottom\":\"20\",\"left\":\"50\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"fwplb74\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Ons doel\",\"header_size\":\"h3\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":\"2\"},\"typography_font_weight\":\"700\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"k509uxw\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"weight\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":\"5\"},\"color\":\"#d76c13\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":\"15\"},\"align\":\"center\",\"gap\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":2}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"divider\"},{\"id\":\"pp0r1br\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Wij adviseren en begeleiden opdrachtgevers bij een verhuizing en (her)huisvesting, op financieel en op operationeel niveau.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\",\"text_color\":\"#ffffff\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"iisnkcg\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"stretch_section\":\"section-stretched\",\"padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"75\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"75\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"#f4f4f7\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"y2rahao\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null,\"padding_tablet\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"50\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"50\",\"isLinked\":false},\"padding_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"10\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"10\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9cnc5lh\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Expertise\",\"header_size\":\"h3\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":\"3\"},\"typography_font_size_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":\"2.2\"},\"typography_font_weight\":\"700\",\"typography_font_size_tablet\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":\"3\"},\"align_mobile\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"e1h0qfm\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>ELPA staat onder leiding van Paul Swolfs, een expert met ruim 20 jaar ervaring in de verhuisbranche.<\\/p><p>Paul heeft 12 jaar bij Van den Berg Verhuizingen (UTS) te Breda gewerkt als planner, projectmanager en salesmanager. Vervolgens heeft Paul als projectmanager en manager sales\\/contractbeheer bijna 8 jaar gewerkt bij projectverhuizer Deudekom Rotterdam\\/Amsterdam.<\\/p><p>De ruime ervaring met grootschalige projectverhuizingen en raamovereenkomsten zorgt ervoor dat ELPA weet wat het inhoudt om een projectverhuizing tot een succes te maken. De ervaring in de verhuissector wordt ingezet bij opdrachten voor zorginstellingen, overheid, scholen en voor bedrijven.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\",\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"100\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"100\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_padding_tablet\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_padding_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":true},\"align_mobile\":\"center\",\"typography_typography\"